title: We're Gonna Do It Again
text: "We're Gonna Do It Again" was a single released on 1 May 1995 by the English <a href="association%20football">football</a> team <a href="Manchester%20United%20F.C.">Manchester United</a> for the <a href="1995%20FA%20Cup%20Final">1995 FA Cup Final</a>. It reached number 15 in the <a href="UK%20Singles%20Chart">UK Singles Chart</a>.
